[normal]Q294[bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Chair:[bold] 
[normal]Professor Adams, I want
[normal] you
[normal] to clarify the distinction that you seem to be drawing between value and price. Without getting into metaphysics and the like, I just presume
[normal]d
