[normal] you would come up with 10 different answers. The question would be: how different are they? That depends on how particular is the form of property. If it is a semi
[normal]-
[normal]detached house, the differences might not be very much; if it is a highland estate, the differences 
[normal]between different valuers 
[normal]might be quite a lot.
[normal]Professor Cheshire[bold]: I am putting no trust in v
[normal]aluers whatsoever
