[normal]Professor Cheshire[bold]: Yes, but not all other countries. It is a continuum. Many countries have no tax reliefs, but we have a series of tax reliefs and subsidies. All European countries have got common agricultural policy payments. Not all of them have inheritance tax relief; not all of them have rate relief.
