[normal]Professor Cheshire[bold]: You are back to taking with one hand and giving back with the other. Why have the tax break in the first place, which, apart from anything else, is leading people who have no association with land or farming to become quite extensive agricultural land controllers?
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q369[bold]&#xa0; 
