[normal]overnments can do to improve the functioning of land markets it is to have decent information systems. I concur entirely about knowledge of the owner and the price being public. It is absolutely essential; otherwise, the difficulty of values or estimates getting out of line with prices becomes worse. Anything that this Committee could do to have that data series reinstated
[normal],
